Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.37,0:22:35.53,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\fnA-OTF Ryumin Pr5 H-KL\fs62\fsp0}Sometimes I wonder again and again
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.75,0:22:41.05,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}跨越數千年 接力棒傳到我們手中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.05,0:22:45.55,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}因漫長道路而目眩 天旋地轉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.17,0:22:51.30,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}一定有尚未發現的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.30,0:22:55.89,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}時刻都在這樣思索 思索
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.89,0:23:01.02,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}不懼失敗 反覆嘗試
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.02,0:23:06.93,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}哭著笑著 追尋光明
