Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.78,0:23:31.88,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}不論去何處 若沒有愛 都無意義
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.88,0:23:37.22,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\fnA-OTF Ryumin Pr5 H-KL\fs62\fsp0}Will I see you again? {\r\blur4}在道路的交點
